text: Cymatonycha fasciata is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Chemsak and Noguera in 1993. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Cymatonycha fasciata. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1993
